" Various Comparing Functions:
"{{{1 atplib#CompareNumbers
function! atplib#CompareNumbers(i1, i2)
   return str2nr(a:i1) == str2nr(a:i2) ? 0 : str2nr(a:i1) > str2nr(a:i2) ? 1 : -1
